About this item

  • Matching top and pant combination set in assorted colors for many Medical office or hospital Departments
  • Total of 10 pockets for convenient organization and access to all essential items
  • Top with v-neck and pant with full elastic waist and side slits at hem for a professional look
  • 55% Cotton, 45% Polyester; medium weight fabric

Description

A style customers keep buying: the 5-pocket top and Cargo pant scrub set by Medgear. For the medical professional who loves pockets, The top features 5 roomy pockets double-stitched to hold everything you need them to carry. The cargo pants feature 5 pockets: two in the front and three at the knee-convenientt for all your storage needs. Made with a soft 55% Cotton, 45% Polyester fabric, this style has been built to perform.

    Tl;dr: if you're on the taller side, BUY THEM! Great, comfy cheap scrubs!

    These are NOT for short girls!!
    I am 4'11", and 150 lbs, so I'm definitely not model thin,I have boobs a gut and thighs (but no butt), so I thought I'd try unisex scrubs!

    I loved the dark purple, and the scrubs are a thicker material and showed no visible panty line, which is more than I can say for other brands. The seams seem solid, and, as it's unisex, the top is definitely boxy. The legs are definitely long! The sizing seems to run a tad or the larger side, but that may just be because it's unisex,and the legs are definitely straight.
    Overall, I'm happy with them, and will look into getting them hemmed!
